C:\Program Files\Microsoft FrontPage\_vti_bin\_vti_adm
C:\WINNT\System32\inetserv\iisadmin\htmldocs\admin.htm  /iisadmin/isadmin


The authentication dll's are structured as follows:

Web Root
    \_vti_bin
     shtml.dll
         \_vti_aut
          author.dll
         \_vti_adm
          admin.dll



